{"tid":393286,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【後悔續咗約？】3香港再劈一成半 無限上網每月306蚊","createTime":"2017-09-09T06:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T10:55:00.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"808d8ee326e17fb89afc27fa39d6d58f3963e3a0","tid":393286,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170908/large/1504874254_6964.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170908%2Flarge%2F1504874254_6964.jpg&h=b2d3d952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n和電香港（215）行政總裁胡超文昨日才笑言「又打仗嘞」，今日隨即繼數碼通（315）昨日劈價三成後，旗下3香港今日再劈一成半，連行政費每月306元推出4.5G不限速無限上網，比數碼通及香港電訊旗下的csl. 都要平10元，如果不計及數碼通的指定轉台優惠，3香港將成全城最平。<br />\n<br />\n胡超文昨日表示，面對減價戰不擔心，指公司網絡承載能力強，密切留意市場發展，隨時可以推新優惠或多數據用量計劃迎戰。3香港的用戶如果後悔早了續約亦不需擔心，3香港表示，由上周五至昨日續約的用戶都可以重新簽訂新合約，享用減價後的月費計劃。<br />\n<br />\n兩日前csl.劈價逾三成，免收150元的「用量皇」無限數據組合服務後，隨即掀起「無限plan」減價戰，同日3香港已經即減2成半，由484元減至366元，如今再減至306元，累計減幅超過三成半。<br />\n<br />\n數碼通昨日亦減價3成，再計針對香港電訊旗下csl.、1010及SUN Mobile轉台用戶額外再減每月18元行政費，月費低至298元，減幅達4成。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n值得留意的是，雖然上述的月費計劃都不會限速，但在《公平使用政策》下，當用戶超越相應流動數據用量上限，其網速或會受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57186305&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57186305%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170908&d=r7mmPrYMUcWEMID77SUNe5nkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=a44fcc6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57186305%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170908&h=26ffdcb7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57186305&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170908</a>"},{"pid":"d7dbafe6efc74ca86007e4b1d5c0cbb879d133a7","tid":393286,"uid":26200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:41:34.000Z","msg":"睇錯一半"},{"pid":"9603866aaf3e86d463e8354b93f1d058c918e9c6","tid":393286,"uid":96757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:44:55.000Z","msg":"屌佢 幾個月前先續左3"},{"pid":"0ead6de51787cd496e52f694db0e9b1c68482ab6","tid":393286,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:47:52.000Z","msg":"早前簽約嘅「舊客」......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb59451892e91cf8417351e4eaecdbb9dbad81d3","tid":393286,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:37:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早前簽約嘅「舊客」......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以打上去講架"},{"pid":"846f05099a67de35362cdc3495865f42f33262fe","tid":393286,"uid":4239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:55:00.000Z","msg":"因為就黎出5G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}